<!-- Content -->
      <p class="small text-wrap">Well done on the win, I only played Euchre a few times about 38 years ago, but I understood both the card game and the subtlety of family dynamics as being tied together. My siblings and I used to play Gin Rummy and the differences in how we played (one sister played with her cards to her chest, and she&#39;s still the reserved one) showed up repeatedly. :) </p>
